@EU_Commission You made the entire Internet more annoying and stupid than it already was. 

LISTEN to the people telling you this. They are correct.

Undo what you did.

@EU_Commission "enhanced rights for users" 

how? I didn't see the user mentioned

In fact didn't you just make data mining legal and banned all photographs at sport events?

@EU_Commission I love Europe but I DESPISE the EU.
why?
Because it is entirely responsible for provoking the rise of the hard right and hard left in Europe. People only turn to the utopians when they are ignored and treated with contempt by their rulers. You are destroying European peace.
